```plantuml
@startuml SocialGouv_archifiltre-docs

actor User
participant "UI (React)" as UI
participant "Main Process (Electron)" as Main
participant "Async Worker (Child Process)" as Worker
participant "File System" as FS
participant "Redux Store" as Store
participant "Export Service" as Export
participant "Sentry" as Sentry
participant "Matomo" as Matomo

User -> UI: Load File System
UI -> Main: ipc:load-filesystem
Main -> FS: Read files/dirs
FS --> Main: File system data
Main -> Worker: Start hash calculation
Worker -> FS: Calculate hashes
Worker --> Main: Hash results
Main -> Store: Update state with files+hashes
Main --> UI: Filesystem loaded

User -> UI: Request Export (CSV/Excel/etc)
UI -> Store: Get current state
Store --> UI: Current filesystem data
UI -> Export: Generate export
Export -> Store: Get additional metadata
Store --> Export: Metadata
Export --> UI: Export file
UI -> User: Download export file

alt Error occurs
    UI -> Sentry: Report error
    Main -> Sentry: Report error
end

opt Analytics enabled
    UI -> Matomo: Track user action
    Main -> Matomo: Track system event
end

@enduml
```